text: The 2019 Ashford Borough Council election took place on 2 May 2019 to elect members of Ashford Borough Council in England.https://www.ashford.gov.uk/councillors-meetings-and- elections/elections-and-electoral-registration/elections-and- vacancies/election-results-archive/borough-parish-election-results-2-may-2019/ This was on the same day as other local elections. ==Result summary== ==Ward results== ===Aylesford & East Stour=== ===Beaver=== ===Biddenden=== ===Bircholt=== ===Bockhanger=== ===Bybrook=== ===Charing=== ===Conningbrook & Little Burton Farm=== ===Downs North=== ===Downs West=== ===Furley=== ===Goat Lees=== ===Godinton=== ===Highfield=== ===Isle of Oxney=== ===Kennington=== ===Kingsnorth Village & Bridgefield=== ===Mersham, Sevington South with Finberry=== ===Norman=== ===Park Farm North=== ===Park Farm South=== ===Repton=== ===Rolvenden & Tenterden West=== ===Roman=== ===Saxon Shore=== ===Singleton East=== ===Singleton West=== ===Stanhope=== ===Tenterden North=== ===Tenterden South=== ===Tenterden St. Michael's=== ===Upper Weald=== ===Victoria=== ===Washford=== ===Weald Central=== ===Weald North=== ===Weald South=== ===Willesborough=== ===Wye with Hinxhill=== ==References== Category:2019 English local elections Category:May 2019 events in the United Kingdom 2019 Category:2010s in Kent
